title: My 10 Books - June 2015 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 10 books, 9 PDFs and 1 ePUB for this month:

01. 30 Essential Yoga Poses - For Beginning Students and Their Teachers by Judith Lasater
02. An Advanced English Practice Course by James Day
03. Math Workout for the GMAT (5th Ed) by The Princeton Review
04. Milady's Nail Structure and Product Chemistry by Douglas Schoon
05. The American Heritage Dictionary of Idioms (2nd Ed) by Christine Ammer
06. The Disappearing Dictionary - A Treasury of Lost English Dialect Words by David Crystal
07. The End Of Science - Facing The Limits Of Knowledge In The Twilight Of The Scientific Age by John Horgan
08. The Rise and Fall of Classical Greece by Josiah Ober
09. The Scientific Secrets of Doctor Who by Simon Guerrier
10. Windows Registry Troubleshooting by Mike Halsey, Andrew Bettany
